00:00:37.071 --> 00:00:43.241
I wanted to make something Delicious and Healthy
with the Apple as a Key Ingredient and finely

00:00:43.241 --> 00:00:45.431
I gave decided to use this Ingredients.

00:00:45.431 --> 00:00:50.761
So let's start cooking this very interesting
and healthy invention.

00:00:50.761 --> 00:00:52.431
For this you will need.

00:00:52.431 --> 00:01:04.221
2 Chopped Apples,50 Grams Cashew nuts.1 Chopped
Capsicum, 2 tbsp Cream, 3 tbsp Oil, 1 finely

00:01:04.221 --> 00:01:12.041
Chopped Onion, 2 Chopped Tomatoes, 1 each
Star Anies, Cinnamon Stick and Red Chilli,

00:01:12.041 --> 00:01:20.691
1/2 tsp Turmeric Powder, 1 tsp Sugar, 1 tsp
Red Chili Powder, Lemon Juice of 1 lemon,

00:01:20.691 --> 00:01:26.671
1 tsp Punjabi Garam Masala, Salt to taste
and some fresh coriander leaves.

00:01:26.671 --> 00:01:36.821
First of all I am going to make the Cashew
nuts and Tomato Puree.

00:01:36.821 --> 00:01:53.401
You can see that, it has became nice and creamy.

00:01:53.401 --> 00:01:56.471
After making puree we have to fry the Apples.

00:01:56.471 --> 00:02:01.181
First of all I am going to Heat oil in a Pan.

00:02:01.181 --> 00:02:03.731
When Oil get heated add the Apples.

00:02:03.731 --> 00:02:12.281
We Have to fry apple for just 2 minutes.

00:02:12.281 --> 00:02:25.691
Now it is soft and perfectly cooked so take
it out.

00:02:25.691 --> 00:02:33.951
Now in the same Oil I am going to add 1 each
Star Anies, Cinnamon Stick and Dry Red Chilli.

00:02:33.951 --> 00:02:35.831
Now add the Onions.

00:02:35.831 --> 00:02:53.100
We have to Saute Onion till they become golden
brown.

00:02:53.100 --> 00:02:57.651
Onion is cooked so add the Turmeric Powder
and Salt.

00:02:57.651 --> 00:03:00.931
Mix this very well.

00:03:00.931 --> 00:03:05.411
Now add the Capsicums.

00:03:05.411 --> 00:03:15.751
After mixing this very well add the Sugar.

00:03:15.751 --> 00:03:24.191
Now Capsicum is little cooked so add the Red
Chilli Powder and again mix this very well.

00:03:24.191 --> 00:03:27.301
Now I am going to add the Cashew nuts and
Tomato Puree.

00:03:27.301 --> 00:03:46.471
After mixing this very well add the Lemon
Juice and Cream.

00:03:46.471 --> 00:04:10.591
Now you have to cook it on a low heat.

00:04:10.591 --> 00:04:26.010
Now I am going to add the Main Ingredient
Fried Apples.

00:04:26.010 --> 00:04:31.401
After mixing this very well add the Punjabi
Garam Masala and freshly Chopped Coriander

00:04:31.401 --> 00:04:33.771
Leaves.

00:04:33.771 --> 00:04:49.741
So this is it mu very Special Invention is
ready to serve.

00:04:49.741 --> 00:05:08.491
Now this is the time to serve this Healthy
and Delicious looking Royal Apple Curry.

00:05:08.491 --> 00:05:25.760
For the Decoration I am going to use the Tomato
and Fresh Coriander Leaves.

00:05:25.760 --> 00:06:01.471
You can serve this curry with Maski paratha
which is also invented by me or Butter Naan

